name: Ember Gift
description: Send to a new player and you both get 100 Embers! Existing player gifts are worth 25 Embers per day. Must be traded to be opened.  Automatically opened on login.  You may only receive one gift from the same player at a time.

name: Ember Award
description: 25 embers!  Automatically consumed on login.  Redeemable if no other ember award turned in on same day.

name: Recruiter Ember Award
description: 100 Embers for recruiting a player! Automatically consumed on login. Can be used immediately!
